## CHRONICLE-LEVEL HUMANITY DOCUMENTATION

For multi-session chronicles, maintain a simple log:

SESSION 1: Humanity 7. Touchstones: Helen, Marcus, Father Mateo.
Major events: First feeding from unwilling mortal — Conviction violated.
Stain accrued.

SESSION 2: Humanity 7 (Stain still active). Remorse work: visited Father
Mateo, confessed. Stain cleared.

SESSION 3: Humanity 7. Major events: Frenzy in Pilsen alley, mortal injured
but survived. Minor Stain. Touchstone Helen learned of the incident from
news; tension developing.

SESSION 4: Humanity 6 (drop from accumulated Stains + Helen's withdrawal).
Felt change: cannot taste shortbread anymore, finds it unsettling.

[continues...]


This log helps both player and AI maintain continuity and lets the player 
see the trajectory of the character's moral arc.
